    • Constructor Detail

      • BasicCentroidCluster

        public BasicCentroidCluster(int id,
                    T centroid)
        Constructs a new Cluster with the given id and centroid. Note the centroid may be modified in the course of running a clustering algorithm, so it may not be a good idea to provide a real data point here (i.e., it's probably best to clone it first).
        Parameters:
        id - an int uniquely identifying this cluster
        centroid - the T
